px; --pf-s-xs:15px;"><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-123a2942" data-pf-type="Column"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-oTLFK lcHmGL pf-409cee5b"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-23d27cee">How to use essential oils for pain relief<br></span></h3><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-a464123a"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-7cee1810">How you decide to use essential oils for pain relief will depend on the type of pain you’re experiencing, as well as your personal preferences. Here are some of our favourite ways to use essential oils for pain relief.&nbsp;<br></span></p></div></div><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-b458a394" data-pf-type="Column"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-oTLFK lcHmGL pf-87e269ed"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-5ecc8e09">Aromatherapy massage for pain relief<br></span></h3><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-69edb458"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-7f7f0300">An aromatherapy massage is a great way to soothe aching or sore muscles and to alleviate pain. You can ask a partner or friend to massage you, visit a qualified masseuse or have a go at self-massage. <br>
<br>It’s important to never apply essential oils undiluted or neat to your skin as they may cause skin irritation. Instead, mix a few drops of essential oil with a tablespoon of carrier oil such as coconut oil or jojoba oil. The mixture can then be massaged into your skin for you to enjoy the analgesic effects of your chosen essential oil.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></span></p></div></div><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-4b34c37c" data-pf-type="Column"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-oTLFK lcHmGL pf-6e7b9736"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-639ff6f6">Inhaling essential oils for pain relief<br></span></h3><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-97364b34"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-3b3b6e7b">Inhaling essential oils is an effective method of pain relief whilst also making your home smell delicious. Simply add a few drops of your chosen essential oil to an aromatherapy diffuser and inhale the aroma. <br>
<br>If you don’t own a diffuser, you can add a couple drops of essential oil to the hot wax of a lit candle to create your own personal scented candle. You can also try adding bergamot oil into a bowl of hot water and inhale the steam. It may seem strange that just inhaling essential oils could help reduce pain, but remember that our smell receptors are closely linked to the limbic system, the part of the brain responsible for emotions and for controlling the stress response, including breathing, heart rate and blood pressure. So it should come as no surprise that simply smelling the aroma of essential oils can have such powerful effects on the body.&nbsp;<br></span></p></div></div><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-61c0d1f4" data-pf-type="Column"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-oTLFK lcHmGL pf-eb40a240"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-afe36916">Aromatherapy bath for pain relief<br></span></h3><p data-pf-type="Paragraph2" class="sc-pkvvt cbrLgP pf-a24061c0"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ptSuy fnmilh pf-2051eb40">A warm bath can have huge benefits if you’re suffering from pain. Hydrotherapy is an effective method of pain relief in itself, especially if your pain is muscular. The immersion, buoyancy and heat that come with a bath are a great way to alleviate pain whilst allowing your body to relax. <br>
<br>Couple this with pain-relieving essential oils to really reap the benefits of an aromatherapy bath. You’ll first need to mix your chosen essential oil with a tablespoon of carrier oil. This will help your oil to disperse effectively throughout the water, avoiding skin irritation. <br>
<br>If you don’t have any carrier oil on hand, don’t worry. You can also mix your chosen essential oil with a tablespoon of full-fat cow’s milk which will enable dispersion.<br></span></p><img sizes="(min-width: 992px) 1200px, (min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 991px) 800px, 400px" data-srcset="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0473/9999/3493/t/3/assets/pf-7f9062db--Bath-diffuser.jpg?v=1606845303 1200w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0473/9999/3493/t/3/assets/pf-7f9062db--Bath-diffuser_800x534.jpg?v=1606845303&resized 800w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0473/9999/3493/t/3/assets/pf-7f9062db--Bath-diffuser_400x267.jpg?v=1606845303&resized 400w" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" class="sc-qZtVr dLIPjF pf-3e7ccb2c pf-img-lazy" data-pf-type="Image2"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-container="true" class="sc-pZopv bjKdkd pf-c6ba79fc" data-pf-type="Section"><div class="sc-pQQXS iWCqut" style="max-width: 1170px;"><div class="sc-qPjXN eYzxUD pf-6418c6ba pf-r pf-r-eh" data-pf-type="Row" style="--pf-s-lg:15px; --pf-s-md:15px; --pf-s-sm:15px; --pf-s-xs:15px;"><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-22966418" data-pf-type="Column"><div class="sc-qPjXN eYzxUD pf-a0462296 pf-r pf-r-align--cm" data-pf-type="Row" style="--pf-s-lg:15px; --pf-s-md:15px; --pf-s-sm:15px; --pf-s-xs:15px;"><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-0a92a046" data-pf-type="Column"><div class="sc-qPjXN eYzxUD pf-b303a80a pf-r pf-r-align--cm" data-pf-type="Row" style="--pf-s-lg:15px; --pf-s-md:15px; --pf-s-sm:15px; --pf-s-xs:15px;"><div class="sc-pbYdQ jklmHY pf-c pf-c-xs--12 pf-c-sm--12 pf-c-md--12 pf-c-lg--12"><div class="sc-pkUyL fTyjzF pf-aa6fb303" data-pf-type="Column"><div class="sc-qPjXN eYzxUD pf-9f1b27f1 pf-r pf-r-eh" data-pf-type="Row" style="--pf-s-lg:15px;